reviewText: SAVE YOUR MONEY! I really did not expect too much when I purchased this dvd. Story had no substance. few lingerie items.

If you like softcore, wait till you can buy this one for $5 or less. There are a couple good scenes but one of the girls was a little weightier than you'd like to see, unless you like them that way, then this will fit your liking.
A nice interaction of actors, and the owner of the store is huge and well performed. Nice softcore movie
